Package: multChernoff
Title: Finite-sample Tail Bounds of Likelihood Ratio Test under Multinomial Sampling
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Richard",
           family = "Guo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ricguo@uw.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2081-7398"))
Description: This package computes finite-sample tail bounds of the likelihood ratio test (LRT) of multinomial sampling. The tail bounds can be used to obtain conservative p-values and critical values, which provides valid inference even when standard Chi-squared asymptotics do not hold.
